items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x01 - Buckley's Goat[/COLOR]
items.summary: Roback convinces Davis to join him in a get rich quick scheme which lands them in serious trouble. Alvarez gets some upsetting news. Roback and Durkin continue their secret affair. Petrocelli finds a new friend in a lost goat.

items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x02 - Finger Lickin' Good[/COLOR]
items.summary: Roback, Davis, and Petrocelli make their way back to base through treacherous desert. Roback makes a grand gesture to help out Alvarez, complicating things with Durkin. Holloway takes a special interest in one of her patients.

items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x03 - Daddy Issues[/COLOR]
items.summary: Roback, Davis, and Alvarez go on a mission to find Qasem. Alvarez makes an unexpected friend. Roback opens up to Durkin, and tries to salvage the fight with Sasquatch.

items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x04 - Trouble in River City[/COLOR]
items.summary: Roback scrambles to keep a promise. Sasquatch reminds the guys they have unfinished business. Holloway has plans to help Qasem's village.

items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x05 - Pain Management[/COLOR]
items.summary: Following an attack on the base, Roback and Davis set out on a dangerous mission for medical supplies and Alvarez gets on-the-job training.

items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x06 - Fight or Flight[/COLOR]
items.summary: Col. Austin brings the hammer down hard on Roback, Davis, and Alvarez. Davis brokers the big fight with Sasquatch. Qasem helps Holloway at her medical clinic.

items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x07 - Mister Fix-It[/COLOR]
items.summary: A visiting dignitary arrives on base. Davis seeks a new side hustle as pressure from home becomes unbearable. Durkin and Sasquatch have a fight about their future.

items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x08 - Do the Right Thing[/COLOR]
items.summary: Roback and Davis attempt a seemingly impossible rescue through an old minefield. SecCorp accelerates their plans. Durkinsteps up to help Petrocelli.

items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x09 - No Good Deed…[/COLOR]
items.summary: The gang discovers the solution to many of their problems, but getting their hands on it won't be easy. Holloway gets a surprise visit. Davis struggles with a major decision.

items.title: [COLOR aqua]1x10 - Close Your Eyes and Jump[/COLOR]
items.summary: The gang heads deep into Taliban country to find the missing cash. Austin makes a final push against SecCorp.
